{"tid":592613,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【巨人殞落】霍金二妻被爆洩「床事」宣示主權","createTime":"2018-03-14T10:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T10:47:14.000Z","uid":66943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"267e42d2916090c768bc1f39e91191581047b7bd","tid":592613,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:44:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180314/1314496/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180314%2F1314496%2F&d=5EFcCi6GraevK3nzQ%2F85iZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=ed765051\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180314%2F1314496%2F&h=ec5463a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180314/1314496/</a><br />\n<br />\n英國物理學家霍金（ Stephen Hawking）逝世，有二段婚姻，而第二任妻子傳曾虐待他！<br />\n <br />\n霍金的第二任妻子，原本也是霍金的護士伊蓮．梅森（ Elaine Mason），2004年、英國《每日鏡報》曾訪問一名前看護，她表示霍金的妻子伊蓮會虐待霍金，「記得有天我看見霍金頸項有一道傷痕。伊蓮一定很粗暴為他剃鬚。那不是普通剃傷，傷口達7.6釐米。」<br />\n <br />\n看護還說：「我們全部人見過霍金受虐待。另一次她把他的手腕重重擲到輪椅上，令他腕骨折斷。另一名看護看見了，就吃了不少苦頭。伊蓮常常擔心別人威脅她的地位。」甚至，看護驚爆伊蓮甚至會讓看護們看她和霍金做愛，「她會全身赤裸坐在他身上。那時，我還以為自己不對，騷擾他們夫妻親熱。後來發現原來很多人都看過。這是為了展示他們還有性關係。」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"a1f377ceecd1db1bfef8b26b09909e06b87e84b9","tid":592613,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:45:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8bd775d9cc217ee1e3d45e5ff3df5974f4226b","tid":592613,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T10:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180314/640_b11c14f330f17d0ef67ce05dec7471ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180314%2F640_b11c14f330f17d0ef67ce05dec7471ce.jpg&h=cbc080d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"